{"tid":1240584,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"齋行無撚用！遊行需要升級！","createTime":"2019-06-18T11:30:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-18T11:38:27.000Z","uid":126612,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"53f68311c33a25c7308b82422411a1a7b652b87d","tid":1240584,"uid":126612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T11:30:35.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">首先！！！</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rnkEuY9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrnkEuY9.png&h=7dfb91cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">星期四 deadline 星期五升級！！！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n達唔到四個要求，星期日再遊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F1b8ok8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF1b8ok8.png&h=b58564a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n但見到和理非們開始有疲態；勇武巴打們又開始心灰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可唔可以試下新玩法呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />和理勇武再融和<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">原因</span></strong></span><br />\n就咁行有個目的地&mdash;&mdash;政總，好多人覺得完成左個路程又唔知再有咩可以做，就好容易走同流失，加上有好多老弱婦孺真係捱唔到咁耐，上星期都有幾個人頂唔順有一個種要危殆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">不如：</span></strong></span><br />\n隊頭行到政總後因為實在太多人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又攰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />全世界一齊坐低休息逼爆港島不撤不散<br />\n<br />\n一黎唔使浪費體力，就咁坐多啲人留到，又有有目標減少人數流失，後join巴打一樣容易搵位zip<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大家輕輕鬆鬆睇書野餐乜都好<br />\n<br />\n二黎又壯觀，人多可以保護大家，同時成百萬人睇你警狗點撚清<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n逼佢10點再回應，唔係成百萬人再一齊去禮賓府or whatever 圍堵林鄭鄭若驊乜乜乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />夠人勝算就大好多"},{"pid":"663db823d90b85888c3c3b27d172fcd969e28769","tid":1240584,"uid":126612,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T11:31:21.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">遊行非佔領<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />只係留力即晚一齊施壓<br />\n<br />\n減少無力感，攞翻主導權</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n遊行有終點心理上好易完成左就走，就算唔甘心都係會流失好多人<br />\n所以，我地改個終點，係一齊坐低等十點，再一齊衝<br />\n遊行升級！<br />\n就算老弱婦孺走哂，都會比前幾次人數多！"},{"pid":"755449ecd0aa781c59aa03837261c4580e99b489","tid":1240584,"uid":126612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T11:31:59.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"d3195d841f2a0732120e141ada56a77c1028a9e7","tid":1240584,"uid":31907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T11:32:18.000Z","msg":"下一次示威的主題應是為「我們仍要真普選」！"},{"pid":"ec8015fe3cb3879354f615843404a1f904be94a1","tid":1240584,"uid":126612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T11:32:24.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"1145fc14d1e2cebf37f98b8e67f8fee0aeba9447","tid":1240584,"uid":126612,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"d3195d841f2a0732120e141ada56a77c1028a9e7","tid":1240584,"uid":31907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T11:32:18.000Z","msg":"下一次示威的主題應是為「我們仍要真普選」！"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T11:33:06.000Z","msg":"救翻兄弟為首要！！！一個不能少！！！！"},{"pid":"0a03535176195a209bb098890fc729e57042e176","tid":1240584,"uid":126612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T11:33:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3db856ca378b7480c99d9ff103adde525c1fc34e","tid":1240584,"uid":126612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T11:33